$ Powershell module console: get-ansiEscapedText

`get-ansiEscapedText` creates text with → Linux/shell/ANSI-escape-sequences.

code {
get-ansiEscapedText 'hello ' ([sgr]::fgRed) ([sgr]::bgGreenBright) ([sgr]::underline) 'world' ([sgr]::reset)
code }

sa:
  This function is found in the PowerShell module → Windows/PowerShell/modules/personal/console[console].
